0712769260dca3394e2a89e54","tid":1776333,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:48:31.000Z","msg":"好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54f909e346c1246df168765701bdea571e23fb2","tid":1776333,"uid":92783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:01:05.000Z","msg":"粉嶺"},{"pid":"ca4805883c58d81c49f702dd409794ca3dd41bd2","tid":1776333,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:03:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尋找黑警性暴力證人/受害者，協助國際遊說</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2Fx%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=eaaed1ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"a16892796cde81ea5dc3377d89867d48ec655709","tid":1776333,"uid":343469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d36031838d4160a4855c882ceb3ea8434c940d15","tid":1776333,"uid":30892,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:48:25.000Z","msg":"邊間？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:08:20.000Z","msg":"順天"},{"pid":"e6b6fec41913bbaeee5b413ede17feac645ec370","tid":1776333,"uid":31986,"like":0,"disl